Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.07,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}一心追求奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:18.23,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}在无尽的黑暗中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.95,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}若在此停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:28.82,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}就再也看不到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.50,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}今宵亦有明月相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.08,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}虽然还未能吐露真意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:38.40,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}但心中一直在呐喊着
